'''阿列克谢·奥克佳布里诺维奇·巴拉巴诺夫'''（{{lang-ru|Алексей Октябринович Балабанов}}，{{bd|1959年|2月25日|2013年|5月18日|}}）<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-22584524 | title = Russian cult film director Alexei Balabanov dies | publisher = BBC News | accessdate = 19 May 2013 | date = 18 May 2013 | archive-date = 2019-07-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190725102127/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-22584524 | dead-url = no }}</ref>是一位[[俄国|俄国]]电影导演、编剧和剪辑师。代表作品有1997年的犯罪片《[[兄弟_(1997年电影)|兄弟]]》及其续集《[[兄弟2|兄弟2]]》，都由[[Sergei_Bodrov,_Jr.|Sergei Bodrov, Jr.]]所主演。影片在俄国国内取得了很大的成功与广泛地流行<ref name="balabanov">{{cite book |  title = The Imperial Trace : Recent Russian Cinema: Recent Russian Cinema| publisher = Oxford University Press | year = 2009| page = 220 | isbn =0199710546}}</ref>。之后，他导演的 ''[[Cargo_200|Cargo 200]]'' (2007) 和 ''[[Morphine_(film)|Morphine]]'' 都很成功<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.heraldsun.com.au/news/breaking-news/russian-cult-film-director-balabanov-dies/story-fni0xqll-1226646275507 | title = Russian cult film director Balabanov dies | work = [[Herald_Sun|Herald Sun]] | date = 19 May 2013 | accessdate = 2014-02-09 | archive-date = 2019-07-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190713075435/https://www.heraldsun.com.au/news/breaking-news/russian-cult-film-director-balabanov-dies/news-story/f371819a26d81150e864f4e2146a439c?nk=798b977784e07947b2d300d376b48458-1563004475 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==生平==
1959年2月25日生于苏联[[叶卡捷琳堡|叶卡捷琳堡]]<ref name="Dies at 54"/>。

1981年毕业于 Translation Faculty of Gorky Teachers’ Training University<ref name="Dies at 54"/>。随后在[[苏联军队|苏联军队]]里担任[[翻译|翻译]]<ref name="Dies at 54"/>。1983年到1987年任Sverdlovsk制片厂的助理<ref name="Dies at 54"/>。后来学习电影导演与编剧课程，1990年毕业<ref name="Dies at 54"/>。1994年，他与 Sergey Selyanov 和 Viktor Sergeyev 一起创建了电影制作公司CTV<ref name="balabanov"/>。

2013年5月18日，他因[[心脏病|心脏病]]发作而病逝<ref name="Dies at 54">{{Cite web | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2013/05/22/movies/aleksei-balabanov-russian-film-director-dies-at-54.html | title = Aleksei Balabanov Russian Film Director Dies at 54 | publisher = New York Times. | accessdate = 23 May 2013 | date = 21 May 2013 | archive-date = 2019-06-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190629060212/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/05/22/movies/aleksei-balabanov-russian-film-director-dies-at-54.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，妻子为服装设计师 Nadezhda Vasilyeva，两人有两个儿子<ref name="Dies at 54"/>，去世前他正在计划拍摄一部有关[[斯大林|斯大林]]的电影。

